rename FinishTile to CheckpointTile and introduced zone numbering system, tiles with the same zone number will be part of the same checkpoint area, zone numbers start at 0 and increment, zone numbers with the highest value represent the final checkpoint (finish line)
terrain between 2 points algorithm complete with basic testing, need thorough tests on wide case range
added minimonza racetrack layout
refactored Terrain to remove slide and chaos - slide is now negative resistance and chaos has been removed from the game

fixed issues with equals and hashcode methods in Tile that were causing issues when removing tiles from the racetrack to overwrite with checkpoints, pretty much at v1.0.0 now, just need to put in checks for all players finishing the race, then final testing/debugging, then can start on styling and AI for v1.1.0
fixed issue regarding next move mouseclick detection being slightly off and detecting in the wrong circle occasionally
